                <h1>Unlocking Ideas: The Background of TED Talks</h1>
                <p>TED Talks originated in 1984 as a conference focusing on technology, entertainment, and design. Over the years, it evolved into a global platform for sharing innovative ideas and inspiring stories. With a commitment to "ideas worth spreading," TED has hosted speakers from various fields, fostering thought-provoking discussions that resonate worldwide.</p>
